{"id":518819269,"lang":"java","time":"7 months, 3 weeks","timestamp":1625671301,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"4 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/518819269/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Edit Distance","memory":"38.6 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int minDistance(String word1, String word2) {\n        int m = word1.length(), n = word2.length();\n        \n        int[][] dp = new int[m + 1][n + 1];\n        \n        for (int i = 0; i <= m; i++)\n            dp[i][0] = i;\n        \n        for (int i = 0; i <= n; i++)\n            dp[0][i] = i;\n        \n        for (int i = 0; i < m; i++) {\n            for (int j = 0; j < n; j++) {\n                if (word1.charAt(i) == word2.charAt(j)) {\n                    dp[i + 1][j + 1] = dp[i][j];\n                }\n                else {\n                    int insert = dp[i + 1][j];\n                    int delete = dp[i][j + 1];\n                    int replace = dp[i][j];\n                    dp[i + 1][j + 1] = 1 + Math.min(insert, Math.min(delete, replace));\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        return dp[m][n];\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"edit-distance"}
